Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: xmpp-logging-handler
Version: 1.0.2
Summary: A python logging framework handler sending to an xmpp server
Home-page: http://www.thisislevelup.com/
Author: Raymond McGinlay
Author-email: Raymond McGinlay
License: GPL v3 or higher
Description: XMPPHandler for Python logging
        ------------------------------
        
        Usage example, assumes gmail.com account.
        
        ::
        
            from xmpp_logging_handler import XMPPHandler
            import logging
            logger = logging.getLogger()
            myHandler = XMPPHandler('SENDING_USER', 'SENDING_PASSWORD', ['raymond@thisislevelup.com',],)
            logger.addHandler(myHandler)
            logging.error('Its broken')
Platform: UNKNOWN
